<l>maṇiyiṟ ṟikaḻtaru nūlpōṉ maṭantai</l>
<l>yaṇiyiṟ ṟikaḻvatoṉ ṟuṇṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is something that is implied in the beauty of this woman, like the thread that is visible in a garland of gems.</l>
